itle>卜街了，只賣得3伙，Hibor 低到0.7%都冇用，低調D，GRAND SEASONS加推138伙 入場價473.9萬起 下周三（5月21日）開售168伙</title><updated>2025-05-21T20:51:30+08:00</updated><author><name>multinumbers123</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-05-21T20:51:30+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_572504195"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_572504195"&gt;甘低息，又專才，又回流，又徹辣，又係地鐵站上蓋，租又升，又有回贈幾十個好消息都係賣3伙。&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;會德豐地產發展的將軍澳日出康城GRAND SEASONS，今日（16日）加推3號價單，涉及138伙，戶型涵蓋一房至三房，入場一房折實價473.9萬元起，折實呎價14,348元起。另外，項目將於下周三（21日）銷售168伙單位。&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31934160&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=1621676934682e0482382688_63343493"/><published>2025-05-21T20:51:30+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>ba35c8fb798f9b97a28cb447d35e4fd8</id><title>初入行會計</title><updated>2025-05-04T02:53:16+08:00</updated><author><name>古正豬豬</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-05-04T02:53:16+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_572245466"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_572245466"&gt;請問中學學歷初入學係唔係做會計文員&lt;br&gt;唔熟電腦有冇可能入行&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31917349&amp;utm_source=festival_fid&amp;utm_medium=110&amp;utm_campaign=1057&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC"/><published>2025-05-04T02:53:16+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>0e84bad1fcd1dc692d23288cd6925b4b</id><title>打工仔辛酸！</title><updated>2025-05-14T23:57:47+08:00</updated><author><name>OL公主</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-05-14T23:57:47+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_572408084"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_572408084"&gt;屋企要供樓，老公失業就快半年，一份工都冇得見！&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;我由25K跌到15K，諗住騎牛搵馬，點知低薪牛工已過試用期，但仲未搵到馬！&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;唔通我要認命做呢份工？&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31927732&amp;utm_source=festival_fid&amp;utm_medium=110&amp;utm_campaign=1057&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC"/><published>2025-05-14T23:57:47+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>cda16872b30da3d6ef3c5009e8151fea</id><title>做緊份兼職，份工本身冇問題，都叫做舒服，但部門主管經常針對新同事。</title><updated>2025-05-16T07:17:36+08:00</updated><author><name>maya1120</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-05-16T07:17:36+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_572424172"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_572424172"&gt;份工做嘅嘢其實唔難，亦都唔係好忙，但係部門主管成日叫啲人做啲其實唔需要咁趕嘅野如果係咁，你哋會選擇做定唔做？&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;但其實其他工作都係有機會遇到呢啲人。&lt;span style="font-size:22px;"&gt;🤔&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31928794&amp;utm_source=festival_fid&amp;utm_medium=110&amp;utm_campaign=1057&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC"/><published>2025-05-16T07:17:36+08:00</published></entry></feed>